OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry night with clear spells, though
OL,7,Flower cloud will build through the
OL,8,Fcentral Belt overnight. Winds light
OL,9,Fand variable in direction.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FAnother generally fair days
OL,12,Fweather in prospect with most dry with
OL,13,Fperiods of sunshine widespread through
OL,14,Fthe morning, before turning hazy from
OL,15,Fthe west during the afternoon. Winds
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
